1136.name: CuSi 3
1136.Applications:
Welding thin plates and or galvanized plates in the car industry and also for cladding CuMn, CuSiMn and CuZn alloys. Suitable for cladding cast iron and un- and low alloyed steels. Examples: 
Automobile industry, art work, cladding on steel, cast iron and copper alloys etc.
1136.Suitable_For: Welding thin steel plates and or galvanized plates in the car industry and also for cladding CuMn, CuSiMn and CuZn alloys. Suitable for cladding cast iron and un- and low alloyed steels.
